snippet.title: Jazz Jackrabbit Holiday Hare 1994
snippet.description: This is the holiday edition of Jazz Jackrabbit, an arcade platform game done by Epic MegaGames in 1994. It features a fast-running green rabbit with a big gun, inspired by Sonic the Hedgehog, Super Mario Bros. and Mega Man. If you couldn't get enough of the original six episodes, you can play extra levels in this game.
